            "title": "港股開市︱初段反彈 恒指升268點報25929點 寧德時代低開0.37%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">外圍股市造好，帶動港股今早初段反彈。恒生指數開市報25929點，升268點或1.05%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報4888點，升66點或1.37%；國企指數以8674點開市，升72點或0.84%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">重磅股普遍回升，滙控(00005)開報141元，升1.59%；友邦(01299)開報88.4元，升1.14%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報125.5元，升1.87%；騰訊(00700)開報497.4元，升1.51%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">寧德時代(03750)將於明天派首季成績表，昨天收市後市場則先傳出，該公司正就配售H股集資約50億美元探討市場興趣；該股今早在競價時段以680元開市，低開0.37%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250602_FI_source-ap_03750-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/06/20250602_FI_source-ap_03750-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">至於已公布配股的靈寶黃金(03330)，今早則開報27.96元，升2.043473%；同樣已訂配售協議的喜相逢(02473)，今早開報1.08元，跌6.9%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中船防務(00317)發盈喜，今早股價開報14.6元，升6.73%；同樣發盈喜的心連心化肥(01866)，股份今早亦高開1.99%，報11.26元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15869678-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87268%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125929%e9%bb%9e-%e5%af%a7%e5%be%b7%e6%99%82%e4%bb%a3%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b0",
